title: Peach is by far my favorite Siggi's flavor.
review: Peach is by far the BEST flavor of Siggi's, IMHO.Really love it.However, NB that like all Siggis yogurts, I have to STIR IN SOME SUGAR or it's otherwise too sour.No big deal, but otherwise its just too tart to enjoy, and I am someone who doesn't like sweets.(Anyway, at 50 cents /lb, its much more economical to stir in your own sugar, rather than have it added by manufacturer who is charging you $3-4 /lb for the end result.)
